    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遥远的未来，大财阀统治着危机四伏的世界。为了平息公众的不满，精英们决定复兴一种古老的娱乐形式：角斗士格斗，将旧时的大场面与尖端科技两相结合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是进入 NCORE 的其中一位幸运角斗士。你的荣耀之路将会是怎样的呢？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >流畅的 PvPvE 战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/ba15c8c42d9e607c259e21c816bd6768.poster.avif?t=1770623091\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/ba15c8c42d9e607c259e21c816bd6768.webm?t=1770623091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/ba15c8c42d9e607c259e21c816bd6768.mp4?t=1770623091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的对手包括：竞技场哨兵、好战的角斗士，以及强大的首领。你可以选择火力全开，也可以选择更隐蔽的策略——你的战斗风格由你决定。但请记住：在 NCORE 中，猎人和猎物的位置可能转瞬即变。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >充满活力的多面竞技场</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/c696c541d11f94535160fcc29b8d3e79.poster.avif?t=1770623091\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/c696c541d11f94535160fcc29b8d3e79.webm?t=1770623091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/c696c541d11f94535160fcc29b8d3e79.mp4?t=1770623091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与昔日的斗兽场截然不同，如今的竞技场是一座高科技的六角竞技场，每个六角格都自成一个世界。军事设施、中世纪城堡，甚至是后丧尸末日城市——规划你的路线、穿越各个地点，并准备好适应竞技场的每次变化。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >变形武器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/d92e282c2bb4a2044bd2a1a3778d8e2e.poster.avif?t=1770623091\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/d92e282c2bb4a2044bd2a1a3778d8e2e.webm?t=1770623091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/d92e282c2bb4a2044bd2a1a3778d8e2e.mp4?t=1770623091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的武器库拥有尖端科技。每把枪都能瞬间变身为近战武器：突击步枪变狼牙棒，霰弹枪变剑，手枪变爪子。明智地切换模式，称霸竞技场。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >团队力量</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/726895c3b95746ed802f60401da4874b.poster.avif?t=1770623091\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/726895c3b95746ed802f60401da4874b.webm?t=1770623091\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307770/extras/726895c3b95746ed802f60401da4874b.mp4?t=1770623091\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与另外两名角斗士组队作战，组成一个独立小队或分头行动，展开混战。随时切换战术、碾压敌人，带领你的队伍走向胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入 NCORE。在这个充满未来感的竞技场中生存下来，成为当代传奇英雄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
